4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%A2u-t%E1%BA%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-19/poem-2cfy4xgyxS7aXx-ZTk2fSg">Tần Châu tạp thi kỳ 19 - 秦州雜詩其十九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-ch%C3%A1nh-s%E1%BB%A9-%C4%90%C3%A0m-hi%E1%BB%87u-th%C6%B0-V%C4%83n-L%E1%BB%85/poem-NxuaJsDusTU7zdUdotF9SA">Thứ vận chánh sứ Đàm hiệu thư Văn Lễ - 次韻正使覃校書文禮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tr%C3%A0-L%C4%83ng-tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-09/poem-6ZjiEuKoza5Da4W4oGfaeQ">Trà Lăng trúc chi ca kỳ 09 - 茶陵竹枝歌其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-NBWGPHKrPwyFe9z3UQCqkQ">Lý Đông Dương</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
